ex;gap:6px;padding:1px 0;font-size:10px;line-height:1.4;"><span style="color:#64748b;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;">✗</span><div style="flex:1;min-width:0;"><span style="color:#94a3b8;font-weight:600;">tier=EXPIRED + grace exceeded</span><span style="color:#94a3b8;"> — tier is &quot;PRO&quot; (not EXPIRED)</span></div></div><div style="display:flex;gap:6px;padding:1px 0;font-size:10px;line-height:1.4;"><span style="color:#64748b;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;">✗</span><div style="flex:1;min-width:0;"><span style="color:#94a3b8;font-weight:600;">tier=EXPIRED (within grace)</span><span style="color:#94a3b8;"> — tier is &quot;PRO&quot; (not EXPIRED)</span></div></div><div style="display:flex;gap:6px;padding:1px 0;font-size:10px;line-height:1.4;"><span style="color:#34d399;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;">✓</span><div style="flex:1;min-width:0;"><span style="color:#bbf7d0;font-weight:600;">past_due</span><span style="color:#e2e8f0;"> — subscription_status is past_due / unpaid → past-due-expiring (Issue 118)</span></div></div><div style="display:flex;gap:6px;padding:1px 0;font-size:10px;line-height:1.4;"><span style="color:#64748b;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;">✗</span><div style="flex:1;min-width:0;"><span style="color:#94a3b8;font-weight:600;">about-to-refill</span><span style="color:#94a3b8;"> — no nextRefillAt or billingPeriodEndAt on workspace</span></div></div><div style="display:flex;gap:6px;padding:1px 0;font-size:10px;line-height:1.4;"><span style="color:#64748b;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;">✗</span><div style="flex:1;min-width:0;"><span style="color:#94a3b8;font-weight:600;">normal</span><span style="color:#94a3b8;"> — a higher-priority rule fired</span></div></div></div><div style="margin-top:6px;font-size:10px;color:#94a3b8;">Result: <b style="color:#7dd3fc;">past-due-expiring</b> (Past Due)</div></div></details>"`;
